Dialogue: 0,0:00:-12.-27,0:00:-10.-26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-10.-24,0:00:-08.-36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-08.-34,0:00:-06.-05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-03,0:00:-02.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-16,0:00:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another big haul today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.51,0:01:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy-sama won't be mad at us,\Nnow that we got all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.35,0:01:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, check it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:02:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Am I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running into someone\Non this wide open sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know who you are, but... water...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might I ask for a cup of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can give you all the money you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem! We'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But not until we see what treasure ya got!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get it open...\NDoes it go like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:03:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can keep my entire boat, if you'd like!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cold front accompanied by low\Nclouds spotted in the southern sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Intense winds and\Nsqualls expected very soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All small boats take\Ncaution not to capsize!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.61,0:03:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya! I'll just take\Nyour treasure now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! You bitch--!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get you for this--!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy's Past!\NEnter Red-Haired Shanks"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the hell're\Nwe gonna reach land?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:04:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows. We're just going\Nwith the wind and waves, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll reach land...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm sure we will, sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it kind of weird that someone\Ntryin' to be King of the Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't even have\Nany navigational skills?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not weird.\NI just drifted around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't you a bounty hunter\Nwho wandered the high seas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no memory of ever even\Ncalling myself a bounty hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set onto the sea in\Nsearch of a certain man...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but then couldn't\Nget back to my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice, so I just went\Nafter pirate ships to earn a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. So you're just lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This straw hat is dear to me--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's been with me through many a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy. I can't give this even to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then take me on your\Nnext voyage, Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna be a pirate too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if you could ever be a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just bein' a good swimmer doesn't\Nmean you'd make a good pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good at fighting too!\NMy punches are like pistols!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He means you're too\Nmuch of a kid, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you're as old as my own kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a kid! I'm a grownup!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Don't get so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Have some juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--See, you are a kid! Ha!\N--That wasn't fair, Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid cheapskate Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... So these are "pirates."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look pretty damn dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're mountain bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we ain't here\Nto tear up the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sell us some booze.\NTen barrels oughta do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.\NI just ran out of alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These pirates seem to be drinking\Nsomething... What is it, water?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, what they're\Ndrinking is the last of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies. Looks like we\Ndrank the whole place dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have this, if you'd like.\NIt hasn't been opened yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an eight million Berry\Nbounty on my head, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One bottle ain't even enough for\Na bedtime drink! Don't insult me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the floor's all wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that, Makino-san.\NDo you have a rag?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems you like to clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe you'll find this more fulfilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not worth our time if\Nthey're out of booze. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, wimps!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Captain?\NAre you hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm fine. No problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He got you good, boss!\N--Talk about lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you laughing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was so uncool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you fight them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many there\Nare or how strong they seem,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're not men-- or pirates--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you laugh after something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand how you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:08:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he only spilled some booze on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing worth getting mad over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eating out of frustration, Luffy?\N--Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what're you eating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That box! Did you eat\Nwhat was in that box?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spit it out! Right now!\NEvery last bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What're you doing, Shanks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you ate was\Nthe Gum-Gum Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gum-Gum Fruit\Nis known as a Devil Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating it turns your body to rubber,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and makes you lose the ability\Nto swim for the rest of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:10:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People were drinkin'\Nand havin' a nice time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the idea, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you make fun\Nof Shanks and his crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say something to offend you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did! Now apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see the looks\Non those pirates' faces?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got covered in booze\Nbut didn't say a word!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are just a bunch of wimps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're nothing but talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.09,0:10:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making fun of\NShanks and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are not wimps!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:11:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making fun of Shanks and\Nthe others! You stupid bandits!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You oughta watch your mouth, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one who's ever made me\Nmad has lived to tell the tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the boy go! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what Luffy has done,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nor do I intend to fight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not offended,\NI'll even pay you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just, please!\NSpare the boy's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to senior citizens\Nto know how the world works.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no, it's too late for him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he's made me angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the bad guys!\NYou mountain apes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lost cause, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can regret all this in the next life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--Please! Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering why\Nthe bar was empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...looks like it's those\Nmountain bandits from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you pirates are still here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been scrubbing the\Nvillage clean this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought your punches\Nwere as strong as pistols?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno why you're here, but\Nyou'd best leave before you get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any closer and he'll\Nshoot your head off, wimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said no closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:13:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me blow your head off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your life on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've drawn your pistol,\Nput your life on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell're you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying those aren't\Nfor threatening people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--N-Now you've done it!\N--These bastards fight dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dirty?\N--Cut the crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, do you think you're\Ndealing with saints or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking at pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You got nothin' to\Ndo with this in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether I'm splattered with\Nalcohol or food or even spit on,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,most of the time I'd just\Nlaugh and forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what the reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,anyone who hurts\Nmy friends has to pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has to pay, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lousy pirates! Kill 'em, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle this.\NShould be easy enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get cocky, bandit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna fight us, then go\Ndrag a warship here or somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on! The kid attacked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a wanted man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A smokescreen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I let my guard down!\NLuffy's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do, guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit freakin' the hell out, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't take us long to find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:15:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.57,0:15:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a clean getaway!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll never expect a mountain\Nbandit to escape onto the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Let me go, you stupid ape!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wish!\NYou're the one who's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you've made me mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys are scum,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't even\Nhit them once! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I got no use for you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:16:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in your debt, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makino-san told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fought for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't cry! You're a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:17:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only an arm. It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just glad you're alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It was a long stay,\Nbut now we part ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bet you'll miss me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, but I won't\Nask you to take me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to become\Na pirate on my own now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't gonna take you anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never be a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I'm gonna gather\Na crew every good as yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm gonna find the\Ngreatest treasure in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:18:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm gonna be King\Nof the Pirates! I'll show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna surpass us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll leave this hat with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come bring it back to me someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've become a great pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our promise, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:18:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna drop it\Nagain if you space out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it important?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bird...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron!\NWhat the hell're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop! You there! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shipwrecked people,\Nat a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop!\NJump in on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you got on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to run us over?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.01,0:20:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're members of Buggy\Nthe Clown-sama's crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This boat is ours now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had no idea you were the\Nfamous Pirate Hunter Zoro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Forgive our rudeness!\N--Forgive our rudeness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you guys,\NI lost sight of my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep padding straight ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yessir!\N--Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing Luffy, he'll manage\Nsomething once he spots land.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what now, Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Captain Buggy finds out a\Ngirl stole our boat and treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this Buggy guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never heard\Nof Buggy the Clown?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:21:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the head of our pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's eaten one of the Devil Fruits,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and is just an\Nall-around terrifying person...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I finally got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Get back here, you!\N--You wench! Give the map back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just stole that\Nchart of the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.47,0:21:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! If we don't get it back,\Nwe're dead meat, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.80,0:21:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna be killed by one\Nof the captain's cannonballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy!\NI see something in the sky above the port!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.42,0:21:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.32,0:22:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the--?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.77,0:22:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.01,0:22:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A person fell from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.11,0:22:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! What are\Ncannonballs flying at me for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.02,0:22:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I'm safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a pretty\Nneat experience I had!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.03,0:22:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I had\Na vision of a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:23:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I always searched\Nfor that miraculous place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before someone else could\Nbeat me to it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.93,0:23:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the world is going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.41,0:23:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before I can even attain my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.41,0:23:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then take me to the time\Nwhen I knew nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that my memories won't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:24:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Being alive while all\Nchopped up is no human technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.71,0:24:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? As a rubber guy, you're\Nplenty of a monster yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.81,0:24:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing makes sense anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.65,0:24:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rubber guy, a chopped-up guy...\NWho are these people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.92,0:24:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Pirates.\N--No! That's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.99,0:24:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.32,0:24:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Terrifying, Mysterious Power!\NCaptain Buggy, the Clown Pirate!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.16,0:24:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
